{"article_id":"ThDjo2y3URCFquM7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The killing of journalist Jamal Khashoggi was planned days in advance ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan has told MPs from his ruling party .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Turkey had strong evidence","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Khashoggi was killed in a premeditated and `` savage '' murder at the Saudi consulate in Istanbul on 2 October .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"He also called for the suspects to be tried in Istanbul .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"He demanded","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Saudi Arabia provide answers","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"about where Khashoggi 's body was , and who had ordered the operation .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The Saudi kingdom has provided conflicting accounts of what happened to Khashoggi , a US resident and Washington Post contributor .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"After weeks of maintaining","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"he was still alive ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"the authorities now say","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"the 59-year-old was killed in a rogue operation .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Erdogan 's address coincided with the start of an investment conference in Saudi Arabia","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"that has been overshadowed by the Khashoggi case .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Dozens of government and business leaders have pulled out ,","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"but Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman appeared at the event on Tuesday .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"Many world leaders have condemned the murder of the prominent Saudi critic","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"and demanded a full investigation .","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"US President Donald Trump says","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"he is not satisfied with the Saudi explanation","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"but he has also highlighted the kingdom 's importance as a US ally .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"CIA director Gina Haspel has been sent to Turkey","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"to review the matter .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Fifteen Saudi nationals ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Mr Erdogan said ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"arrived in Istanbul in three teams , on separate flights , in the days and hours","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"leading up to the murder .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"A day before the killing ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"some members from the group travelled to Belgrad forest , near the consulate","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"- an area","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"searched last week by Turkish police","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"looking for the body .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"He also described","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"how the team had removed the hard drives from the consulate 's surveillance camera system prior to the arrival of Khashoggi ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"who was visiting","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"to obtain documents for his forthcoming marriage .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"A man","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"who looked like Khashoggi ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"wearing his outfit , glasses and a fake beard ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"was among a group","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"who left the consulate the same day as the killing ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"the president added .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"On Monday , CNN broadcast images","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"appearing to show","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that Saudi operative leaving the consulate .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"President Erdogan confirmed","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"18 people had been arrested in Saudi Arabia over the case .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"He told MPs from his ruling AK party","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"the 18 should `` be tried in Istanbul '' ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that `` all those","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"who played a role in the murder ''","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"would be punished .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Mr Erdogan called for an independent commission to be set up","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"he was confident in King Salman 's full co-operation .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"He did not mention the crown prince ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"widely seen as the most powerful figure in the kingdom .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Many believe","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"he ordered the killing ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"although the Saudis deny this .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"BBC security correspondent Frank Gardner says","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Mr Erdogan 's speech was notable as much for what it left out as for what it left in .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"There was no mention of the much-discussed audio tape from inside the Saudi consulate","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Turkish media say","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"reveals gruesome details of the murder .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Trailed as something","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that would expose `` the naked truth '' ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"the speech fell well short of many people 's expectations ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"our correspondent says .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"King Salman chaired a cabinet meeting on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"after which a statement said","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that Saudi Arabia would hold to account those responsible for the killing ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"whoever they might be .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"State media also said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"the king and the crown prince had held a meeting in Riyadh with members of the Khashoggi family , including Khashoggi 's son , Salah bin Jamal .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Mr Erdogan also spoke to family members by phone on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"offering condolences","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"and saying","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"he would do all","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"he could","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to solve the murder .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Saudi Arabia has given conflicting accounts up to now ,","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"initially saying","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Khashoggi had left the building alive ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"then later saying","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"that he had been killed in a `` fist-fight '' inside the consulate .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"On Sunday , the Saudi foreign minister acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Khashoggi had been murdered","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"the leadership had not been aware of the `` rogue operation '' .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"`` The individuals","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"who did this","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"did this outside the scope of their authority , ''","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Foreign Minister Adel al-Jubeir told Fox News .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"`` There obviously was a tremendous mistake made ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"and what compounded the mistake was the attempt","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"to try to cover up . ''","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"that Saudi Arabia did not know where the body was .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"An unnamed Saudi official told Reuters news agency on Sunday","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that Khashoggi had died in a chokehold","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"after resisting attempts","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"to return him to Saudi Arabia .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"His body was then rolled in a rug","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"and given to a local `` co-operator ''","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"to dispose of .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"President Erdogan demanded in his speech on Tuesday for this individual 's identity to be revealed .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"In addition to the arrests , the Saudis say","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"they have sacked two of the crown prince 's aides","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"and set up an organisation , under his leadership ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"to reform the intelligence agency over the killing .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"According to Reuters news agency ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"quoting Turkish and Arabic intelligence sources ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"one of the sacked aides appeared via Skype during Khashoggi 's questioning .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Saud al-Qahtani was quoted as giving the instructions","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"`` bring me the head of the dog '' ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"after the two men traded insults .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"The sources say","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"President Erdogan has a copy of the Skype audio","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"but is refusing to hand it over to the US .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"There 's an odd mixture of unreality and hard-faced pragmatism here .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"Attendees say","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"they 're here","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"to stay with the opportunities","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Saudi Arabia provides for the long haul","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"- however much pressure may be building in the short term .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"But that means that the urgency and outrage over the killing of Jamal Khashoggi","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that is fuelling the news outside","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"is absent here .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"As President Erdogan was delivering his explosive speech ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"the conference here announced $ 50bn","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"( £38.5bn )","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"of investment in 12 mega-deals .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"The contracts were signed with a flourish by a host of foreign CEOs with their Saudi partners to the applause of the audience .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"It was no doubt intended as a resounding vote of confidence in the vision of Saudi Arabia 's future","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"laid out by Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"But that future and those investments could still turn sour ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"despite the mood of optimism and self-approbation","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"exhibited here .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":161,"right":286,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":157,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":152,"right":156,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":145,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":148,"right":150,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":2,"right":146,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":6,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":9,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":158,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":167,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":162,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"